{
  "name": "chat-search",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "IM 跨平台搜尋",
  "category": "I",
  "number": 170,
  "pain_point": "Slack/Teams 訊息找不到",
  "commercial": "⚠️",
  "language": "Python",
  "dependencies": [
    "requests",
    "click",
    "rich"
  ],
  "agent_compatible": true,
  "mcp_ready": true,
  "intent_triggers": [
    "在 Slack 找不到之前的訊息，需要跨平台搜尋",
    "幫我在 Slack 和 Teams 同時搜尋某個關鍵字",
    "三個月前在 IM 聊的某個決策，怎麼找回來",
    "跨通訊平台搜尋工具，同時查 Slack 和 Discord",
    "想搜尋所有頻道關於某個專案的歷史訊息",
    "Slack 免費版搜尋有限，有沒有替代工具",
    "IM 訊息統一搜尋，不用切換不同平台"
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "query": "在 Slack 的 #general 頻道搜尋包含「部署計畫」的訊息",
      "params": {
        "action": "search",
        "platform": "slack",
        "channel": "general",
        "query": "部署計畫"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "同時在 Slack 和 Teams 搜尋「API 規格」相關討論",
      "params": {
        "action": "search",
        "platforms": "slack,teams",
        "query": "API 規格",
        "days": "90"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "搜尋 Alice 在過去 30 天提到的所有 PR 相關訊息",
      "params": {
        "action": "search",
        "query": "PR",
        "author": "Alice",
        "days": "30"
      }
    }
  ],
  "params_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "action": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "author": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "channel": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "days": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "platform": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "platforms": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "query": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "action",
      "query"
    ]
  },
  "license": "MIT"
}
